nodes.label: message
nodes.text: Doctor,    I was in contact with Dr  Person1. He concurs with you re not restarting Lupron. He wants to redo a scan early MM/DD/YYYY (date of my yearly visits) to assess evolution in the 2 newly spot nodal issues, then will decide on what next steps will be. He is not concerned about the renal cysts as possibly cancerous. Best
